data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Beautiful Lakeland subdivision of Manvel, TX.  This 2019 Cervelle has engineered hardwood floors and tile throughout.  Open floor plan with primary bedroom split from the 3 guest bedrooms.  Kitchen open to breakfast bar, living room and dining room.  Guest suite or recreation room above the garage.  Oversized 10 foot Porte-Cochere that parks 2 cars.  Oversized 5 car garage.  Yes, you can park 7 vehicles out of the rain here!  Golf cart friendly community.  Call your Realtor and schedule a tour right away!
